1. Overview

The Nitrologic Foundry Client is a commandâ€‘line research client designed to interact with language models and manage file sharing. Written in JavaScript/TypeScript for execution with Deno, the client leverages several permissions (run, env, net, read, write) and is intended for experimentation with model evaluations, conversation histories, and file submission workflows.

