â€ƒâ€“ The client supports selecting models via the â€œ/modelâ€ command. The list of available models is gathered from multiple API endpoints (configured in the â€œaccounts.jsonâ€ file) and stored in a list (â€œmodelListâ€).  
â€ƒâ€“ It uses tool call functions if the selected model supports the tools interface. Three tool functions are defined:  
